Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun rises today and sets again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:45.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flower bloomed in the morning, falls from its stem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun sets today and rises again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers bloom to fill the land,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but not the flowers of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:22.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be a doctor, since a doctor\Nintroduced me to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:25.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm a Mushi-shi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be so shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I've been told, it sounds\Nlike I'm the right man for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is.
