Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.01,0:02:49.98,ep-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\be1}Those Who Inhale the Dew
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akoya, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:59.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a land across the sea. An open, beautiful land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}People live there really happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go there sometime. I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So don't be so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:14.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.30,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:24.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you staring at the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tides are turning soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:31.89,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The currents are complicated here, and really strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can only get onto the island during the high tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, doesn't look easy to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you a fisherman or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are no fishermen on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:08.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,since there's only one day each month\Nwhen it's safe to set out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing but rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's not much soil. It's a poor island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's just getting by,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the "Ikigami" for hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People, hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.41,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you can't eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:37.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to give it to the Ikigami and\Nhave your sickness taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, get on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.93,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why do we have to be so sneaky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Ikigami" she just mentioned\Nis who I want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was just a normal human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:00.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.96,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's her father beside her; the family head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She receives a "miracle" each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:26.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's the day they can "worship" her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not even breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.38,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.01,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now breathe in those fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:17.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They shall rid your body and soul of illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:22.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is the divine power of the immortal Ikigami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now she returns to her normal self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,By dawn she wakes up as if nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as I heard, but that was still shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It cures people's sickness, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mom died; it didn't help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:49.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We gave the Ikigami almost all of the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:55.60,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her father's family began the Ikigami cult on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:07:01.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was his ancestors that first made it to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:03.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,there have been Ikigamis in his\Nfamily for each generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:15.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People have slowly began gathering to this\Nisland when they learned of the "miracle".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:21.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When one Ikigami dies, a new one appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In less than six months even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:26.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been said that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,there have been people who've been cured
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,of incurable diseases with the Ikigami's fumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:36.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could never believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you playing with an outsider again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, I have something important for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.95,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was about a month after the previous Ikigami died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember that it was on the day\Nof the high tide, like yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:16.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's become someone else, who can't even speak\Nor recall what happened the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:22.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What that meant – I learned after a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.44,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there's been another person who's been cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:30.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing how people can be cured\Nby nothing but suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:37.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya was never a good daughter, but she\Nmust be glad to have made herself useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to find someone who could cure her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left saying I wouldn't be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The family head would be suspicious\Nof me if he found out that I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest you're in trouble too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.18,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:09.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and lead me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.71,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her pulse is abnormally fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her body temperature is much higher than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Light, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There it is, it's a Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It gave birth and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause is a parasitic Mushi in her nasal passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.13,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if she'll be back\Nto normal by removing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she the only subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a few others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all being isolated at the cape over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all the same as Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:30.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They show up once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:40.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The family heads of each generation\Nhave them live here in honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:43.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,as devoted followers who came\Nclose to becoming Ikigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their families are rejoicing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:53.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,saying that "one of their relatives have\Nbeen released from all the suffering".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there was nothing new to be learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:12.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it was a high tide on the\Nday she became sick, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:17.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you think of a place that you\Ncan only get to on a high tide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.24,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cave at the end of the cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:32.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.79,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's infected too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.97,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look around this area for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found two more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:56.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.57,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a remedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:07.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.66,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be over in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.08,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.64,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:37.69,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.65,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.25,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, why did Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya, let's leave the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have three days until the next high tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to pretend you haven't been cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:06.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I like this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:10.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Father would apologize too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:15.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I run, someone else will have to become the Ikigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that you can stop Mushi from\Nbeing abused on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what happened on\Nthe day you became the Ikigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was called up by my father that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:36.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akoya, I picked this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.05,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.68,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't it smell nice? Smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.56,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strong scented flower that looks like bindweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.90,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw them at the cave at the cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were there blooming in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:02.61,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's just be careful not to get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:13.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya, play the Ikigami until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up, can't get back on track?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help but feel anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:46.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was the Ikigami, the sun would\Nset, I'd shrivel up and fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:50.91,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always closed my eyes feeling so content.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But now I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:15:00.21,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd wake up, and it'd be a continuation\Nof yesterday's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:06.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My legs tremble at the long length of time ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were probably living by the Mushi's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:18.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Mushi synchronizes its host's\Ninternal clocks with its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:22.27,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every species has its own longevity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's said that they all live for roughly the same number of heartbeats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means time is more dense\Nfor some than it is for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Mushi has a lifespan of about a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.49,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were experiencing that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.83,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah. That must be why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.63,dialogue,,0,0,0,,every minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.84,dialogue,,0,0,0,,was so breathtakingly fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:59.35,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think fast enough to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:12.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,My heart was so full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:20.87,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be able to go in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.42,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be weakening by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:38.10,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father, I got better for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:39.85,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.98,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagi is back, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:46.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know where he went, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:51.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, today's the high tide, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bindweed in the dark... it really smells.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.80,dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this portion is the Mushi's hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:14.43,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must have a better chance of creating\Noffspring when they nest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.34,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.06,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikigami-sama, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the cave at the cape is. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.03,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, she talked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.58,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.70,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.75,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.59,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, what do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:55.88,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave them, they won't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Men who use Mushi recklessly will slowly go mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll all eventually be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.81,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're unfit to deal with Mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:12.11,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope he has a plan in provoking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.78,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:17.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,After them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.20,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.32,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure their remains will not be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:27.62,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.55,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like Akoya-dono said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:49.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've lost them, but the tide's rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:50.73,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:52.40,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got maybe a half hour left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.74,dialogue,,0,0,0,,People!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found them, it's Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.53,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, stand back, we're gonna open the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.22,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.47,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.26,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:29.02,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I picked this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.94,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.86,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't it smell nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.45,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Smell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.37,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.67,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:58.00,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:03.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only live on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.76,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's infected deeper than the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.52,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.16,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time Akoya looked happy\Nfrom the bottom of her heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:35.46,dialogue,,0,0,0,,was when she was the Ikigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:47.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun rises today and sets again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.48,dialogue,,0,0,0,,A flower bloomed in the morning, falls from its stem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.19,dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sun sets today and rises again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:00.23,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers bloom to fill the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.15,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the flowers of yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:08.28,dialogue,,0,0,0,,but beautiful flowers still.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:17.04,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ginko-san missed the high tide, so he\Nstayed on the island for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that time, he cured all the people on the cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.17,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:30.51,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time the high tide came and the cave opened,\Nsomeone became an "Ikigami" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:35.39,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some people don't appreciate being cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.77,dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll eventually sniff the flower again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akoya said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.82,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:48.07,dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My legs tremble at the long length of time ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:52.33,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're practically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:57.54,dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know what we've got to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.50,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just live normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.92,dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be better off if you can catch some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:09.14,dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dig up the cave so that you can\Nset sail whenever you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:11.72,dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:25.36,dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you've got an endless amount of time ahead of you.
